[{"id":16729,"date":"2025-07-19T17:45:58","modified":"2025-07-19T17:59:13","slug":"aephia-x-galia-merchants-official-shirts-now-live","link":"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/aephia-x-galia-merchants-official-shirts-now-live\/","title":{"rendered":"Aephia x Galia Merchants \u2013 Official Shirts Now Live"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Just in time for Star Atlas Summer \u2014 Aephia shirts are here.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Over the past two years, some of you have walked away from Breakpoint with limited-edition Aephia hoodies and shirts\u2014exclusive swag available only to those attending in person.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Today, on the second day of our 4th anniversary celebrations, that changes!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">For the first time<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">,\u00a0<strong>Aephia-branded clothing is now\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><strong>available to everyone<\/strong>, thanks to our collaboration with <strong>Galia Merchants<\/strong>. Whether you\u2019re here for the vision, the strategy, the camaraderie, or all of it, this drop lets you wear the emblem with pride.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"341\" src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3-1024x341.png\" alt=\"Star Atlas Summer \u2014 July 28 - August 27\" class=\"wp-image-16742\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3-1024x341.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3-300x100.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3-768x256.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3-1320x440.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/image-3.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Star Atlas Summer \u2014 July 28 &#8211; August 27<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>\ud83d\udd25 Limited Edition \u2013 $24.44<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In honor of Aephia\u2019s 4th anniversary, we are offering two <strong>limited-edition shirts<\/strong> in extremely low quantities, made for our most active and dedicated members!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This design has deep roots. It was the <strong>winner of our first internal merch design competition<\/strong>, all the way back in <strong>early 2022<\/strong>. Now, over two years later, it\u2019s finally becoming a reality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udee0 Build. Own. Earn.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>88 White \u2022 44 Black \u2022 Never to be reprinted<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Includes:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\u2713 Build. Own. Earn. \u2014 Aephia multi-faction shirt<br>\u2713 2 matching stickers<br>\u2713 Commemorative NFT collectible<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" data-id=\"16735\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/AEP_BOE-lite.gif\" alt=\"AEP BOE lite\" class=\"wp-image-16735 lazyload\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1000px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1000\/1000;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">AEP BOE Light<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" data-id=\"16734\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/AEP_BOE-dark.gif\" alt=\"AEP BOE dark\" class=\"wp-image-16734 lazyload\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1000px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1000\/1000;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">AEP BOE Dark<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">The Commemorative NFT collectibles (also 3D representations of the shirts)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Commemorating four cycles of Aephian dominance, the Build.Own.Earn. Limited Edition tee marks the journey from humble foundations to interstellar force. Minimalist, symbolic, and bold \u2014 this design honors those who don\u2019t just play the game, but shape it.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Each shirt is a <strong>wearable artifact<\/strong> of Aephia\u2019s fourth cycle\u2014and a tribute to every builder who helped carry the torch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Secure yours before they\u2019re gone. <strong>No reruns.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Unlimited Offerings \u2013 $20.21<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>(Honoring the year Aephia was founded and Star Atlas went public)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"16731\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"Rock to Rocket 1\" class=\"wp-image-16731 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-1536x1536.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1-1320x1320.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_1.png 2000w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/1024;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Rock to Rocket<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"16730\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"Rock to Rocket 2\" class=\"wp-image-16730 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-1536x1536.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2-1320x1320.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Rock_to_Rocket_2.png 2000w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/1024;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Rock to Rocket<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">\ud83e\udea8 Rock to Rocket<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em><em>Available in <em>2<\/em> colors<\/em> <em>(on multiple color shirts)<\/em><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Putting the Machine in War-Machine, Aephia builds what others only dream of. From raw rock to interstellar rocket, we out-mine, out-manufacture, and outlast \u2014 all without firing the first shot.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>We don\u2019t manufacture war \u2014 we build to end it.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A shirt built for builders. Made from a soft, breathable cotton blend, this one\u2019s ready for long hauls, heavy builds, or relaxed post-mission briefings. Whether you\u2019re drilling asteroids or deploying fleets, rep Aephia in unmatched comfort.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"16732\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"Cosmic Currents 1\" class=\"wp-image-16732 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-1536x1536.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1-1320x1320.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_1.png 2000w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/1024;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Cosmic Currents<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"16733\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-1024x1024.png\" alt=\"Cosmic Currents 2\" class=\"wp-image-16733 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-1536x1536.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2-1320x1320.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Cosmic_Currents_2.png 2000w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/1024;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Cosmic Currents<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">\ud83c\udf0c Navigating the Cosmic Currents<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Available in <em>2<\/em> colors<\/em> <em>(on multiple color shirts)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>When the stars dim and the day\u2019s work is done, Aephians gather \u2014 not in silence, but in solidarity. Inspired by our shared hours in the Cantina, Cosmic Currents wraps you in soft, meditative comfort, made for the moments between missions.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Perfect for decompressing after long voyages, recharging in our weekly meetings, or connecting with guildmates across the metaverse. This tee channels the quiet strength of interstellar camaraderie.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A big shout-out to <strong>Brutus<\/strong> for designing all of these shirts! When he submitted the winning design during our merch competition back in February 2022, we knew we had a great designer among us; someone we could trust to shape the future of Aephia\u2019s wearable identity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\ud83d\udc49 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/galiamerchants.com\/product-category\/all\/gm-build\/aep\/\">Get yours now.<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Just in time for Star Atlas Summer \u2014 Aephia shirts are here.<\/p>\n<p>For the first time ever, Aephia-branded clothing is available to everyone, thanks to our collaboration with Galia Merchants. Whether you\u2019re here for the vision, the strategy, the camaraderie, or all of it, this drop lets you wear the emblem with pride.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1}]